{{!--
Perform Treatment Test dialog. Gathers the wound to treat when the physician
runs the `performTreatmentTest` action by hand. Either paste the target
injury's UUID (from its sheet header's "Copy Document UUID" button) — the test
then posts an Accept card to the patient — or describe the wound's severity and
aspect for a GM-directed test that posts an informational result with no button.
The card path supplies the injury UUID in data-scope with skipDialog, so this
dialog never opens there.
--}}
<form>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label>Injury UUID (optional):</label>
        <input type="text" name="injuryUuid" value="" placeholder="Item...." />
    </div>
    <p class="hint">
        Paste the wound's UUID to send the patient an Accept card. Leave it blank
        to run a GM-directed test on the severity/aspect below.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-2col">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>Severity:</label>
            <input type="number" name="severity" value="1" min="1" max="5" step="1" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>Aspect:</label>
            <select name="aspect">
                {{#each aspectChoices}}
                <option value="{{@key}}">{{this}}</option>
                {{/each}}
            </select>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
